descript.abstract: The BaltimoreCity_multiuse_trails layer shows all current and proposed multiuse trails within the Baltimore City limits. It is based on trail shapefiles developed for the Baltimore Bicycle Master Plan in 2006 by Toole Design Group.
descript.purpose: To show current and proposed multi-use trails in the City of Baltimore.
